### 2.7. Content Prioritization

#### Mobile Content Strategy
- ‚úÖ **Show critical content first**
- ‚úÖ **Use progressive disclosure**
- ‚úÖ **Collapse secondary content**
- ‚úÖ **Maintain feature parity (don't hide important features)**

```html
